# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  WHITELIST .gitignore — confidential by default.
#
#  This repo's working folder contains CONFIDENTIAL planning documents
#  (client names, NHS/banking/AML notes, CRM data). To make a leak
#  impossible, we IGNORE EVERYTHING by default and then explicitly
#  re-include only the files the public site needs.
#
#  If you add a new public asset, add a matching "!path" line below.
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# 1) Ignore everything
*

# 2) Re-include the site itself
!.gitignore
!README.md
!index.html
!CNAME
!.nojekyll

# Stylesheets
!css/
!css/**

# Scripts
!js/
!js/**

# Public assets (images + the primary CV only)
!assets/
!assets/favicon.svg
!assets/images/
!assets/images/passport.png
!assets/images/pasted-1782121081671-0.png
!assets/cv/
!assets/cv/Saviour_Henry__AI_Engineer.pdf

# ── Everything else stays ignored, including: ──
#   Crafting SOTA Portfolio Website.md   (confidential chat log)
#   implementation_plan.md               (confidential framing notes)
#   content/  docs/  design/             (internal working files)
#   *.csv                                (private CRM data)
#   assets/images/evidence.jpeg          (not used by the site)
#   Saviour Henry (1)_2.pdf, *_4.pdf, *_Proxify.pdf  (extra/private PDFs)
#   .vscode/  node_modules/  .DS_Store  Thumbs.db
